PRIVACY:
  - Voira processes audio via cloud transcription (Groq Whisper) by
    default. Audio is streamed and never stored on Voira servers.
  - Optional Offline mode (Pro feature) keeps audio on your device.
  - Your dictionary, snippets, and history are stored locally on your
    device.
  - Account email and quota data are stored on Voira backend (EU servers,
    GDPR compliant).
  - Full privacy policy: https://voiravoice.cz (footer → Privacy)

